Title: Add ID to title of host custom attributes on exports
Class: fix
Compatible: incomp
Component: multisite
Date: 1655719898
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.2.0i1

If views with multiple columns "Host custom attribute" were exported, e.g. as
JSON or CSV, the title for each attribute was "host_custom_variable". This was
now changed to "host_custom_variable_ID" to make it easier to distinguish.

Maybe an adjustment of an automated export is needed.
